responses: {"Q0":"Jennifer has been diagnosed with Stage II Lymphoma which is a type of cancer. It will be a difficult journey for her to recovery but it is not impossible. She needs financial support for her medical bills as well as a lot of emotional support as she fights this battle."}
{"Q0":"To see if the story would make me want to donate vs. keeping a potential bonus all to myself"}
